function Start(idActorPlayer, sWorldName)

	Hydra.Wait(1.0)
	local tPlayers = Hydra.QuestGetParticipants()
	for i = 1, #tPlayers do
		Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(convPlayer01, tPlayers[i])
	end

	Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(convPlayer01)
	
	Hydra.Wait(1)
	local tPlayers = Hydra.QuestGetParticipants()
	for i = 1, #tPlayers do
		Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(tPlayers[i], fxWolfHowl)
	end
	
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, sLevelAreaName)

	Hydra.Wait(1)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idActorPlayer) == true then
		Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(convPlayer02, idActorPlayer) -- Global Chatter
		Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(convPlayer02)
		Hydra.Wait(0.5)
	end
	
	local tPlayers = Hydra.QuestGetParticipants()
	
	for i = 1, #tPlayers do
		Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(convMonk01, tPlayers[i])
	end
	
	Hydra.Wait(4)
	
	-- We send an event so that the objective doesn't get marked off until after the conversation.
	Hydra.EventSend("VoiceDone")

end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(actorVani)
	Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(actorOswen)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(actorVani, locVaniFacePlayerShed)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(actorOswen, locOswenFacePlayerShed)
	
	Hydra.Wait(3.5)
	Hydra.ActorSetConversationStatus(actorVani, true)
	Hydra.ActorSetConversationStatus(actorOswen, true)
	Hydra.ActorSetConversationStatus(actorMonkStocks, true)
	
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)

	Hydra.ActorSetUseAlternateName(actorMonkStocks, false)
	
	-- Oswen leaves the building but stays outside the door
	Hydra.QActorWait(actorOswen, 5)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(actorOswen, locOswenShed, "NPC_Walk", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(actorOswen, locOswenShed)
	Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(actorOswen, "NPC_Idle_Stand_Lean")
	Hydra.QActorSetConversationList(actorOswen, "NPC_Frac_Prologue_Oswen")
	
end

function Start()
	-- Vani walks towards Tavern Door
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(actorVani, locTavernDoor, "NPC_Walk_SemiFast", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceActor(actorVani, actorTavernDoor)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(actorVani)
	Hydra.Wait(0.5)
	
	-- Make it look like Vani opened the door
	Hydra.ActorGizmoOperate(actorTavernDoor)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(actorStanis)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(actorIsbel)
	Hydra.Wait(0.5)
	
	-- Move to the final location, face towards player
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(actorVani, locVaniInside, "NPC_Walk_Fast", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(actorVani, locVaniInside)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(actorVani)
	
	Hydra.EventSend("VaniReachedTheFireplace")
end

-- Whether we are on the final phase, which dictaes whether the heartbeat/subzone XP buff application should work
bFinalPhase = true

arCallbacks.unk_28bc3c5:
function Start(idActorPlayer, snoSubzone)

	if bFinalPhase == false then
		local tPlayers = Hydra.QuestGetParticipants()
		
		-- Apply an exp adjustment for pre-Nevesk to ensure players only level up inside Nevesk.
		for i,idPlayer in pairs(tPlayers) do
			Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(S_POWER_EXP_ADJUSTER, "PRE_NEVESK", idPlayer);
		end
	end
end

function Start(flGameTime)
	if bFinalPhase == false then
		local tPlayers = Hydra.QuestGetParticipants()
		
		-- Apply an exp adjustment for pre-Nevesk to ensure players only level up inside Nevesk.
		for i,idPlayer in pairs(tPlayers) do
			Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(S_POWER_EXP_ADJUSTER, "PRE_NEVESK", idPlayer);
		end
	end
end

function Start(idActorDamager, idActorDamaged)
	-- If the player attacks that first wolf, bring his buddies on board
	
	if bFirstWarg == false then
		bFirstWarg = true

		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idActorDamaged)
		Hydra.ActorAddAITarget(idActorDamaged, idActorDamager)
		Hydra.QActorAnim(idActorDamaged, "Generic_Taunt")
		Hydra.Wait(1.5)
		
		for i, Spawner in ipairs(tWolfSpawners) do
			Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdate(Spawner)
			Hydra.Wait(0.15)
		end
	end
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	-- if the player skips past the wolf, do the same as attacking, but faster
	if bFirstWarg == false then
		bFirstWarg = true

		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(actorWolfEating)
		Hydra.ActorAddAITarget(actorWolfEating, idActor)
		Hydra.QActorAnim(actorWolfEating, "Generic_Taunt")
		
		for i, Spawner in ipairs(tWolfSpawners) do
			Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdate(Spawner)
			Hydra.Wait(0.15)
		end
	end
end
